---
// IntroMedica.astro - Versión con contadores distribuidos
---

<section id="inicio" class="relative  bg-transparent py-16 md:py-24 overflow-hidden">
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 relative z-10">
    
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      
      <div class="space-y-8 animate-fade-in">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
          <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
            <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-blue-400 opacity-75"></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-blue-500"></span>
          </span>
          <span>Innovación Médica</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight">
          Tu salud en manos de <span class="text-blue-500 italic">expertos.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
          Contamos con las especialidades más avanzadas y tecnología de punta para brindarte el diagnóstico más preciso.
        </p>

        <div class="flex w-full justify-between md:justify-start md:gap-20 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">
          <div>
            <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">10k+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Pacientes</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">24/7</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Urgencias</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative flex justify-center">
        <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-200 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-50 animate-pulse"></div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-lg">
          <img 
            src="recepcion.webp" 
            alt="Consultorio Moderno" 
            class="rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-2xl border-8 border-white object-cover h-[600px] md:h-[600px] w-full"
          />
          
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white p-4 md:p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl flex items-center gap-4 border border-slate-100 animate-bounce-slow">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-600">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 md:h-6 md:w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-[10px] md:text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">Certificados por la</p>
              <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">OMS</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
  }
  @keyframes bounceSlow {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
  }
  .animate-bounce-slow {
    animation: bounceSlow 4s infinite ease-in-out;
  }
</style>